NK012(na)007:0: rog phur smad las kyi sgrub khog gdug can mthar
NK012(na)007:1: byed rdo rje 'bar ba'i 'khrul 'khor zhes bya ba
NK012(na)007:2: bzhugs so // 'di ni smin slob kyi lag len
NK012(na)007:3: gtso bor bris pa yin pas dpe rgyun la dam
NK012(na)007:4: bzhugs so // par bya'o // rdo rje phur bu'i
NK012(na)007:5: smad las kyi sgrub khog gdug can mthar byed rdo
NK012(na)007:7: bla ma dang dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK012(na)007:8: bde chen ye shes rnam 'gyur las //
NK012(na)007:9: dpag med khro tshogs 'bar ba'i gzis //
NK012(na)007:10: bdud dgra dbyings su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK012(na)007:11: bla ma rdo rje gzhon nur 'dud //
NK012(na)007:12: gdug can ming mthar brlag byed pa'i //
NK012(na)007:13: rdo rje phur bu'i smad las khrigs //
NK012(na)007:14: 'bar ba'i bskal mes bdud sde'i dpung //
NK012(na)007:21: bsgral bya sgrol ba'i yul snying rjes dmigs par bya'o //
NK012(na)007:23: smad las la brten nas dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i thabs drag po mngon spyod kyi las te /
NK012(na)007:24: de la'ang sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK012(na)007:25: sgrub pa'i rim pa dang dngos gnyis /
NK012(na)007:27: lta ba'i gdengs dang bsnyen sgrub las gsum la drod tshad brnyes pa'i slob dpon gyis /
NK012(na)007:28: dpa' brtul che ba drag po'i 'khor dang lhan cig /
NK012(na)007:29: gnag cing rtsub la gnyan pa mngon spyod dang rjes su mthun pa'i gnas su /
NK012(na)007:31: khyad par smad las la dgos pa'i yo byad thams cad tshang bar bsags te /
NK012(na)007:32: mar ngo'i gza' skar dus tshod drag cing rtsub pa'i dus su sgrub cing las la sbyor ba'o //
NK012(na)007:35: las sbyor gyi sgo nas dngos grub kyi bcud blang ba /
NK012(na)007:36: las kyi kha bskang zhing mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK012(na)007:38: stod las kyi bsnyen pa gsum yongs rdzogs su bya ba dang /
NK012(na)007:39: de grub nas smad las kyi bsnyen sgrub la 'jug pa'o //
NK012(na)007:41: dug phur nag po'i las byang rtsa bar /
NK012(na)007:42: phun sum tshogs pa'i slob dpon gyis //
NK012(na)007:43: bsnyen pa rnam gsum rdzogs byas nas //
NK012(na)007:45: ye shes kyi lha nye bar bsnyen pa /
NK012(na)007:46: dam can nye bar bsnyen pa /
NK012(na)007:47: ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa gsum ste /
NK012(na)007:48: sgrub thabs dang sgrub khog ltar bya ba las /
NK012(na)007:49: phyi ma gnyis kyi 'dzab khang dbye ba dang bstod pa ni /
NK012(na)007:50: ye shes lha'i bsnyen pa 'dra la /
NK012(na)007:52: dam can bsnyen pa'i tshe rgyas par so so'i bskul gyi bkol byang 'og nas 'byung ba ltar ram /
NK012(na)007:53: bsdu na de thun tha ma gcig pur sbyar zhing thun gzhan rnams la /
NK012(na)007:54: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:55: ces sogs bab lngas bskul lo //
NK012(na)007:56: ngan sngags kyi tshe sgrub thabs ltar 'dod pa'i don
NK012(na)007:57: la gsol ba gdab pa nyid kyis bskul ba yin
NK012(na)007:58: no // de ltar bsnyen pa gsum gyis ye shes
NK012(na)007:59: kyi lha grub pa'i rtags sgrub khog tu bshad pa
NK012(na)007:60: no // ltar dang / dam can grub pa'i rtags su rab srung ma'i sku dngos su ston /
NK012(na)007:62: tha ma dgra bo'i glo snying phyung ba'am bla 'khrid pa dang bsad pa sogs 'byung /
NK012(na)007:63: ngan sngags kyi rtags su rab dgra bo'i glo snying phyung ba /
NK012(na)007:65: tha ma dgra bo'i bla bsad pa rnams dngos nyams gang rung dang /
NK012(na)007:66: rmi lam du yang rgya mtsho 'thung ba /
NK012(na)007:68: nyi zla spar bas 'dzin pa sogs 'byung ba'o //
NK012(na)007:69: gnyis pa de grub nas smad las kyi bsnyen sgrub la 'jug pa ni /
NK012(na)007:71: dgra bgegs rnam gnyis bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK012(na)007:72: drag po'i gnas su dkyil 'khor bri //
NK012(na)007:74: stod las su bsnyen pa yongs rdzogs kyi lugs kyis bsnyen pa gsum la rtags thon pa dang /
NK012(na)007:75: stod las kyi sgrub pa bsdus te /
NK012(na)007:77: smad las kyi dkyil 'khor e ka dmar nag gi tshul du bzhengs te /
NK012(na)007:79: dbus na pho brang e yi dkyil //
NK012(na)007:80: zla gam dbang chen rak+ta'i rgya mtsho 'khrug /
NK012(na)007:81: chos sku skye med mu khyud zlum por 'khyil //
NK012(na)007:82: mkha' dbyings bcu drug e yi mtha' bskor te //
NK012(na)007:83: dug gsum 'joms phyir thod pa tshar gsum dang /
NK012(na)007:84: bar khyams dang ni ye shes sgo bzhir ldan //
NK012(na)007:85: phyi rol khor yug bskal pa'i me ris bskor //
NK012(na)007:87: lte ba gru gsum mthing nag /
NK012(na)007:89: mu khyud thod ra dkar po rnams 'dra bas de'i
NK012(na)007:90: phyir gru chad kyi thig la reg par bskor ba'i
NK012(na)007:91: mu khyud mthing ka zlum po'i nang gzhi dmar smug
NK012(na)007:92: la / phyogs mtshams brgyad du e gru gsum zur phyir bstan re dang /
NK012(na)007:93: de dag gi dbal kha brgyad la gru gsum logs phyir bstan re ste /
NK012(na)007:94: gru gsum mthing nag bcu drug bri /
NK012(na)007:95: gru chad khrag mtsho khyams ser po /
NK012(na)007:97: thod pa tshar gsum gyi rtsig pa sogs de phyin stod las ltar ro //
NK012(na)007:98: de nas phyag rgya dgod pa ni //
NK012(na)007:99: lha phur nyi shu lnga las /
NK012(na)007:100: dbus kyi gru gsum la gtso phur /
NK012(na)007:101: phyogs mtshams kyi gru gsum brgyad la khro bo brgyad /
NK012(na)007:102: dbal kha'i gru gsum brgyad la za byed brgyad /
NK012(na)007:103: steng 'og gi khro bo za byed dang bcas pa
NK012(na)007:104: shar nub kyi nang thod ra'i rtsar gru gsum re
NK012(na)007:105: la 'god cing / yum rnams kyi phyag rgya dmar
NK012(na)007:106: nag gru gsum nyid yin pas gud du dgod mi
NK012(na)007:108: phur bu logs su yod na gtso bo /
NK012(na)007:110: za byed de yab nyer gcig po so so'i mdun
NK012(na)007:111: ngos su yum phur rnams yab la zhal phyogs pa'i
NK012(na)007:113: de phyin sgo bzhir sgo phur /
NK012(na)007:114: khyams la dam can sde lnga'i phur bu bco lnga rnams dgod /
NK012(na)007:116: mgyogs phur sum cu yang 'du bya'o //
NK012(na)007:117: de nas dam rdzas bsham pa ni /
NK012(na)007:118: dkyil 'khor gyi mdun du 'bru sna'i rjen la dpal
NK012(na)007:119: chen po'i 'das gtor sha lnga bdud rtsi lngas brgyan
NK012(na)007:120: pa dar nag gi gdugs phub pa stegs la bkod
NK012(na)007:121: pa'i g.yas g.yon du sman raka /
NK012(na)007:122: shar lhor shwa na bzhi'i gtor ma wa khyi 'phar spyang gi shas brgyan pa /
NK012(na)007:123: lho nub tu bswe mo bzhi'i gtor ma khrag zhag 'o ma mar bzhii'i dbus mtheb kyus brgyan pa /
NK012(na)007:124: byang shar du re ma ti bzhi'i gtor ma nal
NK012(na)007:125: bu'i sha khrag dang khrag sna snying snas brgyan cing
NK012(na)007:126: tshil chen gyis kha bkab la rtse mor rma bya'i
NK012(na)007:128: nub byang du ging gsum gyi gtor ma sha gzugs
NK012(na)007:129: dang stag gzig ras ma mda' dar le brgan rnams
NK012(na)007:130: kyis brgyan pa rnams gta' gtor te /
NK012(na)007:131: rgyun gtor kyang ci 'byor pa dang /
NK012(na)007:132: mchod rdzas tshogs kyi yo byad rnams kyang bsham mo //
NK012(na)007:139: grog mkhar rnams kyi sa dug khrag dang bong gcin
NK012(na)007:140: sogs kyis sbrus pa'i brub khung me ri rtsang dmar
NK012(na)007:141: gyis bskor zhing / ro g.yam la rgya gram bris pas kha bcad pa'i nang du /
NK012(na)007:142: ling+ga byad thag sngo dmar gyis bcing zhing yugs skra
NK012(na)007:143: ske la btags pas khams gsum rnam rgyal gyi phur
NK012(na)007:144: bur brtod de mgo lho nub la bstan nas gan
NK012(na)007:147: dur khrod kyi 'jag ma yug skra'am ro ras kyi skud pas bsdams pa'i rus shing la /
NK012(na)007:148: dgra la khang sa'am dri ma drug gang rnyed grog
NK012(na)007:149: mkhar gyi sa dang bsres pa dug chus bardzisa pa'i
NK012(na)007:150: 'dam dang / 'dre la gnas rten gyis lug thug gi chus bardzisa pa'i 'dam ste /
NK012(na)007:151: sngar gyi rus shing la khyad par gyi 'dam gyi
NK012(na)007:152: 'dag pa byugs nas dgra gzugs ji lta ba dang
NK012(na)007:153: / 'dre la rmi lam du gang byung gi gzugs khru gang ba gcig byas la /
NK012(na)007:154: de'i snying gar dgra 'dre'i ming byang bris pa lte
NK012(na)007:155: ba la tshon skud kyis bcings nas 'jug par bya
NK012(na)007:157: bri gzhi dgrar ro ras dang 'drer dug shog la /
NK012(na)007:158: dug khrag thal chen rnams dang sbyar ba'i snag tsha dang /
NK012(na)007:159: mtshon grir bsad pa'i mi rkang gi rus pa'i smug
NK012(na)007:160: gus ling+ga'i gzugs bris pa'i snying gar n+ri'am tri'i mthar
NK012(na)007:168: 'doms rnams su lha dang dbral ba nas stob pa'i bar gyi gab pa'i sngags drug po dang /
NK012(na)007:169: ling+ga'i tha ma bzhi snying gcig tu dril ba'i sngags kyis bar med du 'khor ba bri'o //
NK012(na)007:170: gzhan yang lha dbye la sogs pa'i las drug gi rdzas dang /
NK012(na)007:171: mnan bsreg 'phang ba'i rdzas so so'i bkol byang ltar
NK012(na)007:172: bsags pa sogs 'dir dgos pa'i yo byad thams cad
NK012(na)007:174: de ltar bcas kyi bshams bkod rnams tshar nas /
NK012(na)007:175: bsnyen sgrub kyi cho ga ni /
NK012(na)007:177: thun mong las rnams rdzogs byas nas //
NK012(na)007:178: bdag nyid lha yi nga rgyal gyis //
NK012(na)007:179: spyan drangs mchod cing bsnyen pa 'bul //
NK012(na)007:180: drug drug sum cu rtsa drug gis //
NK012(na)007:181: sgrub pa'i las rnams rdzogs byas la //
NK012(na)007:182: drag po'i las la sbyar bar bya //
NK012(na)007:183: zhes gsungs pas smad las kyi bsnyen sgrub las gsum
NK012(na)007:184: po de zla ba'i nag phyogs kyi nyer gcig nas
NK012(na)007:185: dgu stong gi bar la rdzogs par byed pa ste
NK012(na)007:186: / de la dang po bsnyen pa ni /
NK012(na)007:187: smad las kyi mgo non du ye shes lha'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK012(na)007:188: dam can gyi bsnyen pa gnyis kha gso ba yin pas /
NK012(na)007:189: dus bzhi 'am drug tu las gzhung bsrang ba stod las dang 'dra ba las 'dir bzlas pa'i tshe /
NK012(na)007:190: zhag dang po la sgrub thabs ltar bskyed rim dang sbyar ba'i ye shes lha'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK012(na)007:192: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs ka
NK012(na)007:193: nas sngags kyi 'od zer 'phros pa dam can rnams
NK012(na)007:194: kyi snying gar phog pas bskul te sha rul la
NK012(na)007:195: sbrang ma 'du ba ltar 'thibs kyis byon nas rang
NK012(na)007:196: dbang med par las byed par bsam la /
NK012(na)007:197: bzhi snying gcig tu dril ba'i sngags kho na bazla'o //
NK012(na)007:198: zhag gnyis ka'i thun tha ma'i rjes chog gi tshogs
NK012(na)007:199: tha ma dang 'brel bar brub khung gi ling+ga la'ang
NK012(na)007:201: sras kyi phur bskor gyis gzir zhing khro bcu'i sngags kyis thun re yang 'phang ste /
NK012(na)007:204: nyer gsum nas nyer brgyad kyi bar zhag drug la riim par /
NK012(na)007:205: zhag dang po la lha dang phral ba /
NK012(na)007:206: gnyis par gzugs la dbab pa /
NK012(na)007:207: gsum par byad du gzhug pa /
NK012(na)007:208: bzhi par smyo ru gzhug pa /
NK012(na)007:209: lnga par rdul du rlog pa /
NK012(na)007:210: drug par zhal du stob pa /
NK012(na)007:211: de re re la'ang drug drug sum cu rtsa drug tu nyams su len pa ste /
NK012(na)007:212: thams cad la thun gyi las gzhung bsrang ba sngar ltar las /
NK012(na)007:213: bsnyen pa'i dod du las drug po skabs thob kyis sbyor ba ste /
NK012(na)007:214: zhag dang po lha dang phral ba la'ang drug las /
NK012(na)007:216: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:217: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:218: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:221: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK012(na)007:222: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK012(na)007:223: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK012(na)007:226: gu gul dang tshil chen gyi gsur gyis bdug /
NK012(na)007:227: bya rog dang 'ug pa'i dang ru thogs pas phyir 'byed pa'i phyag rgya yang bya /
NK012(na)007:229: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+r+aihdan+da h+aum phata /
NK012(na)007:232: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs las khro chung dpag
NK012(na)007:233: tu med pa dang 'od zer mgar gyi tsh+wa tsh+wa
NK012(na)007:234: lta bu spros pas skyob byed kyi lha thams cad
NK012(na)007:235: bya rog 'ur rdos bskrad pa bzhin du byer bar
NK012(na)007:237: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs kyis
NK012(na)007:238: dgra bgegs 'di skyob byed kyi lha dang phrol cig
NK012(na)007:240: zhag gnyis par gzugs la dbab pa la'ang drug las /
NK012(na)007:242: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:243: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:246: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK012(na)007:247: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK012(na)007:248: phob cig rnam par gzir bar byos //
NK012(na)007:251: sdigs phur thogs nas 'bebs tshul gyi phyag rgya bya zhing yungs kar gyis brab /
NK012(na)007:253: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee a be sha ya a be sha a ya h+aum phata /
NK012(na)007:256: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs las sprul ba dang
NK012(na)007:257: yang sprul dpag tu med pa spros pas dgra bgegs
NK012(na)007:258: rnams rang dbang med par bkug ste ling+ga la gnyis
NK012(na)007:259: med du bstim par bsam mo //
NK012(na)007:261: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs kyis dgra bgegs 'di'i rnam shes gzugs la phob cig /
NK012(na)007:263: zhag gsum par byad du gzhug pa la'ang drug las /
NK012(na)007:265: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:266: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab /
NK012(na)007:269: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK012(na)007:270: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK012(na)007:271: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK012(na)007:274: tshon skud sna lnga dang yugs skra'i skud pas phyir
NK012(na)007:275: bzlog tu dkri zhing yan lag 'khyig tshul gyi phyag
NK012(na)007:277: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee sh+r+ai g+h+ram +aa na ya h+aum phata /
NK012(na)007:280: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs las sprul pa yang
NK012(na)007:281: sprul dpag med spros pas dgra bgegs rnams ri dwags
NK012(na)007:282: rgyar tshud pa ltar bcings par bsam mo //
NK012(na)007:284: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs kyis
NK012(na)007:285: dgra bgegs gnod byed 'di gru gu thul du chings
NK012(na)007:287: zhag bzhi par smyo ru gzhug pa la'ang drug las /
NK012(na)007:289: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:290: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:293: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK012(na)007:294: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK012(na)007:295: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK012(na)007:298: dug sna dang da du ra'i skyo ma blugs shing khar byug tshul gyi phyag rgya bya'o //
NK012(na)007:300: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h+aum phata /
NK012(na)007:303: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs sprul pa yang sprul
NK012(na)007:304: dang bcas pa rnams kyis smyo dug gi char phab
NK012(na)007:305: pas dgra bgegs rnams smyo zhing 'bog par bsam mo
NK012(na)007:307: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs kyis dgra bgegs 'di smyo ru chug /
NK012(na)007:309: dran pa nyams su chug cig /
NK012(na)007:311: zhag lnga par rdul du brlag pa la'ang drug las /
NK012(na)007:313: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:314: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:317: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK012(na)007:318: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK012(na)007:319: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog /
NK012(na)007:322: rdo rje tho ba dang gtun khung gru gsum thogs te bar du brdung ba'i phyag rgya bya /
NK012(na)007:324: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee mo ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK012(na)007:327: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs sprul pa yang sprul
NK012(na)007:328: dang bcas pas rdo rje ri rab kyi tho ba
NK012(na)007:329: thogs nas dgra bgegs kyi lus rdul phran bzhin du
NK012(na)007:332: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs kyis
NK012(na)007:333: dgra bgegs gnod byed thal ba'i rdul du rlogs shig
NK012(na)007:335: zhag drug par zhal du stob pa la'ang drug las /
NK012(na)007:337: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:338: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:341: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK012(na)007:342: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK012(na)007:343: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK012(na)007:344: bsgo ba'i bka' la nyan par gyis //
NK012(na)007:347: bra ma'i hom chag gang ba zhig brtsigs par me
NK012(na)007:348: sbar la ling chung gcig sreg cing ling ro stob
NK012(na)007:351: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee b+hin+da ya b+hin+da ya h+aum phata /
NK012(na)007:352: ces bzla zhing ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK012(na)007:353: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha tshogs sprul pa yang sprul
NK012(na)007:354: dang bcas pas dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag rus pa
NK012(na)007:355: rnams dgyes pa'i rkan sgra dang bcas te bzhes pa'i
NK012(na)007:356: tshul gyis bsdigs par bsam mo //
NK012(na)007:358: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs kyis
NK012(na)007:359: dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag rus pa thams cad lhag
NK012(na)007:362: gnyis pa las sbyor gyi sgo nas dngos grub kyi bcud blang ba la gnyis te /
NK012(na)007:366: phur bu mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyud las /
NK012(na)007:367: rab kyis dngos su khug par 'gyur //
NK012(na)007:370: tha mas nyams dang rtags 'ong ste //
NK012(na)007:371: de tshe brdeg pa'i dus la bab //
NK012(na)007:372: ces pa ltar lha rtags dang dgra rtags gtan la phebs shing /
NK012(na)007:373: bla mi 'gyur ba'i rtags dngos su byung na phral du phur bu gdab pa'i las la 'jug ste /
NK012(na)007:374: gdab pa'i dus gnad kyang dgra'i bla sha ba yin na srod /
NK012(na)007:380: ra nyi nub kyi thog tu gdab par bya ba yin no //
NK012(na)007:381: de la 'dir nub tha ma la sgrub zhag bdun pa /
NK012(na)007:382: dgu stong gi dus su las la sbyor te //
NK012(na)007:383: las kyi gzhung bsrang ba rdzogs par byas nas //

NK012(na)007:1053: 'dra'i 'khor 'bum gyis bskor bas mnan te nam yang
NK012(na)007:1054: thar ba med par bsam zhing /
NK012(na)007:1056: gnyis pa gso ba rnam pa gsum gyis las kyi mjug bsdu ba la /
NK012(na)007:1062: bsgrub bya dmigs su bsal ba la las drag po rtsom pa'i dus yin na /
NK012(na)007:1063: las nam grub pa dang gdod gso bar bya yi /
NK012(na)007:1064: las ma grub par gso ba snga na las myur du mi 'grub pa'i rgyu yin par gsungs so //
NK012(na)007:1065: bsgrub bya dmigs bsal med na phur bu btab pa'i rjes nyid la gsos pas chog go //
NK012(na)007:1066: gnyis pa yul ni gsum ste /
NK012(na)007:1070: gsum pa dgos ched kyang gsum ste /
NK012(na)007:1072: drag po'i las kyi rnam smin rgyud la mi gos par bya ba'i ched do //
NK012(na)007:1074: phyag rgya'i lha rnams gzir mnan gyi dme ba'i las
NK012(na)007:1075: la sbyar bas bsod nams kyi don du mi rung
NK012(na)007:1076: ba'i phyir bzod par gsol ba'o //
NK012(na)007:1078: snying rje byang chub kyis zin pas bsgral bya rnams
NK012(na)007:1079: la phan gdags shing skyob par bya ba'i phyir ro
NK012(na)007:1080: // gso ba'i thabs la'ang gsum ste /
NK012(na)007:1081: las dang bya ba'i gso ba ni /
NK012(na)007:1082: k+ai la ya bcu gnyis kyi tan+t+ra las 'byung ba'i cho ga zhib mo lta bu'o //
NK012(na)007:1083: man ngag gis gso ba ni /
NK012(na)007:1084: dmigs bya phur bu bdag gsum gyi byang chub kyi
NK012(na)007:1085: sems ljang dmar mthing kha'i 'od rnam pa gsum dbyer
NK012(na)007:1086: med 'od kyi thig le gcig tu bsdus pa mi
NK012(na)007:1087: dmigs par sbyor ba'i man ngag rig pa mchog gi
NK012(na)007:1088: rgyud las gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK012(na)007:1089: 'dir phrin las rdo rje gzhon nu nyid nas gsungs
NK012(na)007:1090: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis gso ba la phyag bzhes
NK012(na)007:1095: gsang sngags kyi byin gyis brlab bo //
NK012(na)007:1097: a b+hi ts+aar+ya dus la bab bo //
NK012(na)007:1098: brnag pa de kho na la'o //
NK012(na)007:1100: k+ai la ya brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas /
NK012(na)007:1101: gong du btab pa'i phur bu'i khro bo de dag
NK012(na)007:1102: ye shes kyi 'od zer gong bu'i rnam par gyur
NK012(na)007:1103: pa tshur 'dus bdag la thim pas sku gsung thugs
NK012(na)007:1104: kyi dngos grub thob ste rang nyid gdod nas lhar
NK012(na)007:1105: gsal ba de'ang sku che la yan lag rags pa
NK012(na)007:1106: che btsan 'gran zla dang bral bar bsam pa'o //
NK012(na)007:1108: gong du btab pa'i phur bu de phyung ste dbal
NK012(na)007:1109: nas bzung la k+ai la ya nyer gcig bzla zhing
NK012(na)007:1110: klad la lan gsum bskor bas khams gsum phur bus
NK012(na)007:1111: gang / de thams cad slar 'dus pas stod khro
NK012(na)007:1112: bo zhal gsum phyag drug pa smad phur bu'i rnam
NK012(na)007:1113: pa can sku ri rab ltar brjid che ba las
NK012(na)007:1114: gang / / ye shes kyi me 'od 'bar zhing 'ur sgra drag po sgrogs par bsgoms pas /
NK012(na)007:1115: lha rnams la nyes pas mi gos shing gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK012(na)007:1118: zhes brjod cing phur bu sgril zhing btab ste /
NK012(na)007:1119: k+ai la ya lan bco brgyad bzlas pas phur bu'i
NK012(na)007:1120: ye shes kyi 'od zer gzas po'i khams bco brgyad
NK012(na)007:1121: kyis mtshon pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma
NK012(na)007:1123: sems nyid rdul phran dwangs ma'i thig le yi ge h+aum gi rnam par gyur pa /
NK012(na)007:1124: a yam zhes a las byung ba'i zla dkyil gyi steng du bzhag ste /
NK012(na)007:1125: yam las byung ba'i rlung gis btegs na /
NK012(na)007:1126: phata ces 'og min gyi zhing du spar te //
NK012(na)007:1127: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams su
NK012(na)007:1128: thim nas rdor sems kyi sras su skyes par bsam
NK012(na)007:1129: pa ni gnas spar ba ste /
NK012(na)007:1130: gnas lung dpyang thag gi cho ga thugs rje rjes 'dzin gyi phur gdab ces kyang bya'o //
NK012(na)007:1131: rgyun gyi yi dam nar mar byed pa'i phur gdab
NK012(na)007:1132: kyi dus su 'di nyid gong gi tshe lung gi
NK012(na)007:1133: mjug tu sbrel bas chos kyi dbyings su sgrol ba'i
NK012(na)007:1134: thabs la mkhas pa'i sbyor ba ste bsgral las kyi
NK012(na)007:1135: gtso bo nyid tshang bar 'gyur ro //
NK012(na)007:1136: gzhan yang tshogs gtor tshe 'gugs dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing
NK012(na)007:1137: rgyun ting bya ba sogs thun mong gi rjes chog
NK012(na)007:1138: rnams las byang dang sgrub khog las 'dor len gyi
NK012(na)007:1139: dmigs phyed pa shes par bya ba gces so //
NK012(na)007:1140: gsum pa grub pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK012(na)007:1141: 'dir gzhan stobs kyi thabs lam las byung ba'i khyad
NK012(na)007:1142: par tsam ma gtogs thob bya'i ngo bo sngar bshad
NK012(na)007:1143: pa bzhin no // ngaga brjod bsam 'das dbyings ngor dgra med kyang //
NK012(na)007:1144: rnam rtog 'khrul snang dabnga gis dgrar langs pa //
NK012(na)007:1145: chosa kun bden med rtogs pa'i 'khrul 'khor gyis //
NK012(na)007:1146: dapala chen dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i dbyings sgrol shog /
NK012(na)007:1147: rdo rje phur bu rog lugs lha nag gi smad
NK012(na)007:1148: las sgrub khog gdug can mthar byed rdo rje 'bar
NK012(na)007:1149: ba'i 'khrul 'khor zhes bya ba 'di yang kong po
NK012(na)007:1150: bde chen steng nas so ston khu dbon gyis don
NK012(na)007:1151: gnyer chen pos bskul zhing gzhis bzhugs khu dbon gyis
NK012(na)007:1153: gter chen chos kyi rgyal po yab sras rigs kyi
NK012(na)007:1154: cod pan du thob pa'i smyos ban d+harma sh+r+ais nyis
